        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span>When you pull up the hood of this nondescript gray cloak (an&nbsp;Interact action), you become drab and uninteresting, gaining a +1 item bonus to Stealth checks and to Deception checks to Impersonate a forgettable background character, such as a servant, but also taking a –1 item penalty to Diplomacy and Intimidation checks.<br></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span> envision, Interact; <strong>Frequency</strong> once per day; <strong>Effect</strong> You pull the cloak’s hood up and gain the benefits of nondetection for 1 hour or&nbsp;until you pull the hood back down, whichever comes first.</span></p>",
